There was one other sighting in Moose Jaw on or around April 12th 2011
divs: sighting detailsfollowing the report of numerous star-like objects during aurora borealis on the 12th, at dawn (5:05 am) a close encounter with a diamond\star-like object flew over the city. it was heading south east. it's a wonder if anyone else noticed it or how competent the local military installation's personnel or are informed on these matters. it wouldn't surprise me if it was one of ours.
Summary: Following the report of numerous star-like objects, at dawn a close encounter with a diamond/star-like object flew over the city
